---
/**
 * Small monospace all-caps kicker — a quiet top-line label that tells the
 * reader "this is meta" (ref id, section, provenance).  Pairs well with
 * a HeroHan immediately below in the same band.
 */
---
<span class="card-kicker"><slot /></span>
<style>
  .card-kicker {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>
